text: Swampers (or Killians Ferry) is an unincorporated community in Franklin Parish, Louisiana. The name was collected between 1976 and 1980 by the United States Geological Survey, and entered into the Geographic Names Information System on June 4, 1980.USGS GNIS Feature Detail Report: Swampers Harris Cemetery is located in Swampers. Interred there is Regnal Wallace, the former Louisiana farm broadcaster of radio and television. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Franklin Parish, Louisiana Category:Unincorporated communities in Louisiana
